<normalizedToken originalValue="Atlântica">Atlantica</normalizedToken>
in Bahia.
</paragraph>
<paragraph pageId="0" pageNumber="1">
<emphasis bold="true" pageId="0" pageNumber="1">BRAZIL. Bahia</emphasis>
